al in the women's long jump three years ago.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Commonwealth champion, however, finished in fifth position this time around.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999985456994752, \"rank\": 1.1362441350239595e-06, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brume confessed he was hampered by injury.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, it was an amazing experience for me,\\\" Brume told Making of Champions.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back to where I am coming from, I did not compete much this year because of injuries.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even up to today, I also competed with an injury, but I am glad that I made it this far.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy with myself and thankful to God.\\\"\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"EPL: He will score goals - Ten Hag hails Man United star despite missing open net  Friendly: Iheanacho, Ejuke named in Sevilla's squad for Liverpool clash  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins Best Coach award  Paris 2024 Olympics: Sports Minister apologises to Nigerians after disastrous outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Team Nigeria officially finishes without single medal  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's last medal hope Reuben crashes out in Wrestling  Paris 2024 Olympics: Reuben launches Nigeria's final search for medal  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815,